response.Q0: At first, I studied how clicking works and then figured that the last step is the most important. Thereafter, my plan was to always check the last node, if the last node had a higher value, my chances of getting more money were higher, and vice versa. Eventually, I also clicked on middle and first nodes to get an idea of what direction I needed to take.
response.Q1: Yes, I initially clicked on the first nodes in the first few rounds, but as I got better understanding of the game, I realised that clicking on the last node in each direction was a better strategy.
